---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="seven-requirements"
  description="Your Seven Requirements assessment is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Seven Requirements are ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your assessment"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Seven-Requirements-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>Seven governance requirements that persist if every framework disappears. Self-assessment scoring, industry baseline, and the two absences the entire industry has not considered.</p>
    <p>Most organizations score between 0 and 4 out of 21. The requirements do not change when the regulation changes.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/seven-requirements" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Score honestly</h3>
      <p>Score what exists in your architecture today. Pay attention to Requirements 5 and 7 - the two the entire industry scores zero on.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the assessment page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/level-6-governance-toolkit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Complete the audit</h3>
      <p>The Ostrom Score, Identity Violation Assessment, and Agent Consent Architecture complete the Level 6 Governance Audit.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See the bundle &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/governance-audit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
      <p>If your score surfaces structural gaps, a Governance Diagnostic can help close them.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See audit options &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your results.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
